Determining which shoe will be best for the shape of your foot is no easy task. If you’ve got flat feet, you know the struggle that is trying to find an attractive shoe that is comfortable enough for all-day wear. Instead of stuffing your favorite flats with padded insoles so you can actually wear them without cringing, we’ve found 18 stylish shoes that will cure your flat feet woes. HuffPost may receive a share from purchases made via links on this page.